name: Nike Dunk Low White/Black
description: From the school-spirited College Colors Program to the vibrant Nike CO.JP collection, Nike Dunks have seen many colorways since the design’s inception in 1985. But with each new colorway, the Dunk’s classic color-blocking has remained in some capacity. Nike put its timeless color-blocking to work with the Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black.

name: Nike Dunk High White/Game Royal-Total Orange
description: The Nike Dunk High Game Royal pays homage to the original 1985 University of Kentucky colorway of the Nike Dunk. It features a white leather upper with Game Royal overlays and Swooshes. A matching sole and woven tongue label add the finishing touches.

name: Jordan 1 Retro AJKO Ghost Green/Ghost Green
description: Jordan teamed up with pop icon Billie Eilish to release two signature Air Jordan Retro silhouettes in the fall of 2021. The first of the two, the women's Air Jordan 1 AJKO Billie Eilish Ghost Green (W), draws a resemblance to one of Eilish's most well-known hairstyles and motifs.

name: Nike Dunk Low Yellow Strike/Yellow Strike-White
description: The women's Nike Dunk Low Yellow Strike (W) features a white leather upper with pale yellow blotted overlays and plush Yellow Strike suede Swooshes. Matching two-tone soles and woven tongue labels carry this pastel palette across the finish line.

name: Jordan 1 Retro AJKO Storm Blue/White-Black
description: In a traditional AJKO canvas fabrication, the Air Jordan 1 KO Storm Blue features a white upper with Storm Blue overlays and black Swooshes. From there, a matching woven Nike Air tongue label and sole completes the retro design.

name: Nike Dunk Low White/Green Glow-White
description: After releasing the Nike Dunk Low Orange Pearl (W) and Nike Dunk Low College Navy (W) in the spring of 2021, Nike delivered yet another women’s exclusive Dunk Low this season with the Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W). While the Green Glow is the first of its kind, its usage of traditional Dunk color blocking adds a familiarity to the design.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wash Orange/Wash Orange/Wash Orange
description: The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Wash Orange features a grey leather, suede, and mesh upper with teal panels and reflective underlays. At the base, a thick Wash Orange Boost midsole contrasts cool tones found in the upper.

name: Jordan 12 Retro White/Black-University Red
description: The Air Jordan 12 Twist features a white tumbled leather paneled upper with a pebbled leather mudguard. From there, red metallic Jumpman side tabs and eyelets, black woven heel tabs, and a sculptural sole completes the design.

name: Nike LD Waffle SF Blue Void/White-Obsidian-White
description: The Nike LDWaffle sacai Fragment Blue Void combines the best of both sacai and Fragment's aesthetics. The mesh, leather, and suede construction of the LDWaffle represents sacai's experimental outlook, while the black and Blue Void palette is more reserved, similar to the utilitarian look that many of Fragment's collaborations have.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Seafoam/Healing Orange-White
description: The women's Air Jordan 1 High Seafoam (W) arrives in a smooth white leather construction with Seafoam Durabuck overlays and Swooshes. On the laces, crisp bronze trimming stands out against the design's subtle coloration.

name: Nike LD Waffle Net/Orange Blaze-Deep Red-Green Bean
description: Taking cues from the Nike Air Max 1 CLOT Kiss of Death, the Nike LDWaffle sacai CLOT Orange Blaze boasts an off-white translucent and suede upper with Deep Red and Orange Blaze snake-textured Swooshes. From there, a two-toned stacked sole and doubled tongue amplify sacai's unique design aesthetic.

name: adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Blue Tint/Black
description: The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 MNVN Blue Tint features a Blue Tint nylon upper with reflective graphics and details throughout the design. A thick black Boost sole and tongue adds the finishing touches to the hiking-inspired design.

name: Nike Dunk Low Midnight Navy/Championship Grey-White
description: The Nike Dunk Low Georgetown arrives with a smooth grey leather upper with Midnight Navy overlays and Swooshes. From there, matching woven Nike Air tongue tags, heel tabs, and Air soles complete the retro design.

name: adidas Yeezy Slide Pure/Pure/Pure
description: DISCLAIMER: US and UK sizing is the same and does not require any conversion.

name: adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion/Vermillion/Vermillion
description: The adidas Yeezy Foam RNNR Vermillion features an all-red one piece EVA foam construction with oval cut-outs to provide ventilation. At the base, a cushioned footbed offers support and stability.

name: Jordan 4 Retro University Blue/Tech Grey-White-Black
description: Jordan Brand paid homage to MJ’s alma mater with the Air Jordan 4 University Blue. The University Blue colorway draws a close resemblance to the extremely rare Air Jordan 4 UNC PE that was given to Tarheel student-athletes in 2019.

name: adidas Yeezy 500 Clay Brown/Clay Brown/Clay Brown
description: The adidas Yeezy 500 Clay Brown presents an array of materials commonly found in hiking shoes designed to withstand the great outdoors. It is constructed of a Clay Brown mesh upper with leather and suede overlays that wrap the silhouette. A sturdy adiPRENE sole adds a responsive feel to the trail-ready design.

name: Jordan 12 Retro Black/Black-Bright Crimson-White
description: With black leather and Durabuck paneled construction, the upper of the Air Jordan 12 Utility sets the stage for its glittery sole to shine. The sole is composed of Nike Grind, a material made of a collection of recycled materials originating from leftover Nike manufacturing materials.

name: Jordan 6 Retro Black/Light Graphite-Dark Grey-Bordeaux
description: The Air Jordan 6 Bordeaux features a two-tone black and grey Durabuck upper just like the original Jordan 7 Bordeaux. From there, the signature Bordeaux geometric pattern is prominent on the inner-facing tongue and sock liner. Jumpman embroidery on the heel and a semi-translucent outsole complete the retro look.

name: adidas Yeezy Slide Green Glow/Green Glow/Green Glow
description: Constructed of bright Glow Green EVA foam, the adidas Yeezy Slide Glow Green provides lightweight durability with a luminous look. From there, strategic groove placement on the underfoot enhances traction and comfort.

name: Nike Dunk Low University Red/White-Total Orange
description: The Nike Dunk Low Championship Red features a University Red leather upper with white leather overlays and Swooshes. A matching sole and woven tongue label adds the finishing touches to this retro design.

name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG White/Multi-Color-Total Orange
description: Jordan Brand encourages sneaker customization with the Air Jordan 1 Prototype.

name: Jordan 4 Retro White/Tech Grey-Black-Fire Red
description: The Air Jordan 4 Retro White Oreo features a white leather and mesh upper with hits of Tech Grey on its eyelets and midsole. From there, a red Jumpman logo is embroidered on the tongue, adding a pop of color to the neutral-toned design.

name: Nike Dunk High White/Midnight Navy
description: Also known as the Nike Dunk High Villanova, the Nike Dunk High Championship Navy displays classic color-blocking with a white leather upper and Championship Navy overlays. From there, a matching woven tongue label and sole complete the retro design.

name: adidas Yeezy 450 Dark Slate/Dark Slate
description: With a simplified two-piece construction, the adidas Yeezy 450 Dark Slate features Dark Slate foam sole that clasps a monochromatic sock-like Primeknit upper. From there, thick rope laces add the finishing touches.

name: New Balance 2002R Rain Cloud/Grey
description: The New Balance 2002R Protection Pack Rain Cloud features a grey mesh upper with tonal jagged suede overlays and a reflective New Balance logo. From there, a cream Nrgy midsole and grey outsole complete the design.

name: Crocs Pollex Clog Cucumber
description: In a monochromatic Cucumber color scheme, the Crocs Pollex Clog Salehe Bembury Cucumber is composed of dramatic, fingerprint-like concave ridges, allowing for multi-directional traction. While the design doesn’t have nearly as many holes as a traditional Croc, the remaining holes serve a purpose: they are located on high-heat areas of the foot for increased breathability. A removable canvas strap at the ankle provides wearers with options for styling.

name: Jordan 1 Mid Black/University Red-Black-White
description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned (2020) takes the classic Banned colorway of the high-top Jordan 1 and applies it to the mid-cut sneaker.

name: Jordan 1 Low OG White/Neutral Grey-Particle Grey
description: Arriving in its original form, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG Neutral Grey features a white leather upper with Neutral Grey Durabuck Swooshes. A white and Neutral Grey sole completes the design.

name: Nike Dunk Low Yellow Strike/Yellow Strike-White
description: The women's Nike Dunk Low Yellow Strike (W) features a white leather upper with pale yellow blotted overlays and plush Yellow Strike suede Swooshes. Matching two-tone soles and woven tongue labels carry this pastel palette across the finish line. The women's Nike Dunk Low Yellow Strike (W) released in August of 2021 and retailed for $110.

name: Jordan 1 Retro AJKO Storm Blue/White-Black
description: In a traditional AJKO canvas fabrication, the Air Jordan 1 KO Storm Blue features a white upper with Storm Blue overlays and black Swooshes. From there, a matching woven Nike Air tongue label and sole completes the retro design.

name: Nike Dunk Low White/Green Glow-White
description: After releasing the Nike Dunk Low Orange Pearl (W) and Nike Dunk Low College Navy (W) in the spring of 2021, Nike delivered yet another women’s exclusive Dunk Low this season with the Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W). While the Green Glow is the first of its kind, its usage of traditional Dunk color blocking adds a familiarity to the design. The upper of the Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W) is composed of white leather with Green Glow leather overlays and Swoosh logos. From there, a woven Nike label is sewn to the tongue and a white “NIKE” is embroidered on the heel. A white midsole and Green Glow outsole completes the design. The women's Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W) released in April of 2021 and retailed for $100.
